Package com.github.tadukoo.util.view.components

Class TadukooButton.TadukooButtonBuilder

java.lang.Object
com.github.tadukoo.util.view.components.TadukooButton.TadukooButtonBuilder
Enclosing class:
TadukooButton
public static class TadukooButton.TadukooButtonBuilder
extends java.lang.Object
Builder to be used to create a TadukooButton. This is the abstract version to be extended in subclasses of FormField. It has the following parameters:
TadukooButton Parameters
Name Description Default Value or Required
text The text to use on the Button Defaults to null
icon The icon to use on the Button Defaults to null
actionListener The action to perform on click of the Button Defaults to null
shapeInfo The ShapeInfo to use on the Button Defaults to null
